div.div: Select day of event (will default to today)
Select the type of game for the day and course
Table will load showing all infor for the given course (tee's, hole hcps, distances, etc...)
- on the table there will be options to select a player/tee and enter all scores
- as you enter the scores the card will automatically get marked up with net/gross values and handicap details for the holes you receive a stroke on

If playing a team game there will be an option to select the team number also and team details will display at the bottom of the page with their respective scores and which ones were taken for the total
